Activities:
  • Create this text inside the process "Core A"
  • Create an empty Note element
  • Connect the Note element to the process
  • Right click on the relation between the process and the Note and select "Link this Note to an Element Feature.."
  • Set Feature Type to "Element Note"
  • Now this text will be shown in the Note element
Use this feature to visualise the documentet activities inside an process if needed.
